Examples
--------

 Getting information from Evince project hosted in bugzilla.gnome.org

 1- Using the command line

 $ bicho --db-user-out=[USER] --db-password-out=[PASS] --db-database-out=prueba bg https://bugzilla.libresoft.es/buglist.cgi?product=CVSAnalY

 2- Using a config file (broken in master version)

  2.1 Content of the configuration file

##[General]
type = 'bg'
url = 'https://bugzilla.gnome.org/buglist.cgi?product=evince'
debug = False
delay = True

##[DatabaseOut]
db_driver_out = 'mysql'
db_user_out = [USER]
db_password_out = [PASSWD]
db_database_out = 'bicho_database'
db_hostname_out = 'localhost'
db_port_out = '3306'

  2.2 Execution

  $ bicho --cfg=config.sample

 3- help

  $ bicho --help
